{"tid":567113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"來自Nike.com的色覺實驗","createTime":"2018-02-20T14:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T14:32:57.000Z","uid":73338,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"da5bf828ccb8b77ee98979559e23c92105c7eb3c","tid":567113,"uid":73338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:30:41.000Z","msg":"首先大家可以認住下面條褲隻色，接下來我會變個魔術俾大家睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nike.com.hk/product/823364-451/detail.htm?locale=zh-hk&amp;cp=hkns_em_070116_u_TRANS_na01\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nike.com.hk%2Fproduct%2F823364-451%2Fdetail.htm%3Flocale%3Dzh-hk%26cp%3Dhkns_em_070116_u_TRANS_na01&d=LG5iZRcf1akFTiRMjndvrZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=55f1c7a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nike.com.hk/product/823364-451/detail.htm?locale=zh-hk&amp;cp=hkns_em_070116_u_TRANS_na01</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jybgZX2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjybgZX2.png&h=99c3148b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟毒撚一名，有散光近視但冇色盲，平時好少出街買衫<br />\n<br />\n新年前為應節上網買左條褲同對鞋過年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LscfM0W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLscfM0W.png&h=76d3c59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先開箱試身，點知一拎上手就變左條咁嘅野...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7elA7Ozt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7elA7Ozt.png&h=ee97337c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n心諗究竟係我買嗰時撳撚錯色定nike玩鳩我<br />\n<br />\n我confirm完應該唔係自己問題之後決定上nike online cs搵人開年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9RGhL7J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9RGhL7J.png&h=53ab634a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得到嘅答案係...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vg0Q1yZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVg0Q1yZ.png&h=f91dfcdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(恰我讀得書少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n最後我有提出事件中誤導成份建議佢地搞搞佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vzrZjTy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvzrZjTy.png&h=7d989174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係咩大事同最後係咩色對我黎講其實並唔重要，都會照著<br />\n<br />\n但係可唔可以唔好再玩鳩毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">btw如果一陣肥屍又衝入黎左左右右麻煩捉佢幫Ivan祭旗唔該。</span></span>"},{"pid":"8e08246d1af2677635c94bf6f64282ecade584cb","tid":567113,"uid":61560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T14:32:57.000Z","msg":"黑曜色(黑)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}